Imprisoner/Predator/Choran:



Imprisoner watched with interest as Demolition tried to escape his cell.
"I'm afraid our weapons were deactivated, save our optics.  But this brig was 
modified to surpress power from our optic weapons."

Predator and Choran nodded dumbly at Imprisoner, their hopes up at feeling 
the constant shakes due to the CF being bombed all day long.
